title: User query: Plan description from client LLM
log: Create a Wayang plan that checks the total purchases in 2025 from creditors with "VVS" in their name. It must also be creditors that do not have "SLETTET" in their name. Output in descending. I want creditor_id, creditor name and total price of each in my output. Output in textfile.

operations.table: (SELECT purchase_id, creditor_id, invoice_date, invoice_line_price FROM factpurchases) as X
(SELECT creditor_id, name FROM creditor) as X

log.thoughts: Filter purchases to 2025, sum invoice_line_price per creditor, filter creditors with 'VVS' and without 'SLETTET', join and sort descending by total, then write to textfile.

title: Class: PlanMapper Mapped plan finalized for execution

data.table: (SELECT purchase_id, creditor_id, invoice_date, invoice_line_price FROM (SELECT purchase_id, creditor_id, invoice_date, invoice_line_price FROM factpurchases) as X) as X
(SELECT creditor_id, name FROM (SELECT creditor_id, name FROM creditor) as X) as X
